@FeeNominalService_HostAddress = https://localhost:7139

### Authentication Endpoints

### Login
POST {{FeeNominalService_HostAddress}}/api/v1/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@example.com",
  "password": "Admin123!"
}

### Refresh Token
POST {{FeeNominalService_HostAddress}}/api/v1/auth/refresh
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "refreshToken": "your-refresh-token-here"
}

### Revoke Token
POST {{FeeNominalService_HostAddress}}/api/v1/auth/revoke
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer your-jwt-token-here

{
  "refreshToken": "your-refresh-token-here"
}

### Validate Token
GET {{FeeNominalService_HostAddress}}/api/v1/auth/validate
Authorization: Bearer your-jwt-token-here

### Surcharge Endpoints

### Calculate Surcharge
POST {{FeeNominalService_HostAddress}}/api/v1/surcharge/calculate
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer your-jwt-token-here

{
  "amount": 100.00,
  "sTxId": "test-transaction-123",
  "mTxId": "merchant-transaction-456",
  "country": "US",
  "region": "CA"
}

### Batch Calculate Surcharges
POST {{FeeNominalService_HostAddress}}/api/v1/surcharge/batch
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer your-jwt-token-here

[
  {
    "amount": 100.00,
    "sTxId": "test-transaction-123",
    "mTxId": "merchant-transaction-456",
    "country": "US",
    "region": "CA"
  },
  {
    "amount": 200.00,
    "sTxId": "test-transaction-789",
    "mTxId": "merchant-transaction-012",
    "country": "US",
    "region": "NY"
  }
]

